Dependencies for Ubuntu
=======================
- Open a terminal and type:
  % sudo apt-get install build-essential
  % sudo apt-get install subversion
  % sudo apt-get install ruby
  % sudo apt-get install libgstreamer0.10-dev 
  % sudo apt-get install libaspell-dev 
  % sudo apt-get install libavcodec-dev libavformat-dev 
  % sudo apt-get install libqt4-gui qt4-qmake qt4-dev-tools

Note: If you are not using Ubuntu, check for the equivalent
      packages for your Linux distro

Get the source and compile
==========================
- Firstly, the core library:
  % svn checkout svn://svn.berlios.de/ktoon/trunk/kom
  % cd kom
  % ./configure --prefix=/usr
  % make
  % sudo make install

- Secondly, the application:   
  % svn checkout svn://svn.berlios.de/ktoon/trunk/ktoon 
  % cd ktoon
  % ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/ktoon
  % make
  % sudo make install
  % sudo cp launcher/ktoon /usr/local/ktoon/bin

Animation time!
===============
- Execute:
  % /usr/local/ktoon/bin/ktoon &
  
